# HARISREE PURCHASE APP — CURSOR RULES v3
# New Harisree Agency, Thrissur, Kerala
# Stack: Flutter (Riverpod) + FastAPI + PostgreSQL

## Single source of truth
- Purchase draft: `purchaseDraftProvider` in `lib/features/purchase/state/purchase_draft_provider.dart`
- No `setState` for core purchase data (only UI-only: step index, local errors, controllers)

## PROTECTED (avoid breaking without intent)
- `purchaseDraftProvider`, `purchaseTotalsProvider`, `purchaseStrictBreakdownProvider`
- `tradePurchasesListProvider`, `suppliersListProvider`, `brokersListProvider`
- Backend route path prefixes: `/v1/businesses/{business_id}/...` (add new routes, do not rename existing without migration)

## ALWAYS DO
- HapticFeedback.selectionClick() on main nav; HapticFeedback.mediumImpact() on save
- `ref.invalidate(...)` after create/update/delete that affects lists
- Shimmer or placeholder blocks for loading (not `SizedBox.shrink()` for main content)
- Confirm before delete / discard with unsaved changes
- Min 1 char for search fields; 300ms debounce on search inputs
- `NumberFormat.currency(locale: 'en_IN', symbol: '₹')` for money in UI
- PDF header background: #0D9488; company fallback: NEW HARISREE AGENCY

## NEVER DO
- HSN as mandatory on catalog create (HSN is optional for traders)
- Snackbars for form validation (use inline text)
- Emojis in PDF body
- New duplicate purchase/item flows; extend the canonical path only

